    Title: Ecclesiasticus
    Locus: XXXIX 20
Tags:
  - Invocation=The Glory of the Name
  - Beauty-Peace=Beauty=Music
---
Magnify his name, and give glory to him with the voice of your lips, and
with the canticles of your mouths, and with harps.
